Titolo: Ghostrunner

Anno: 2020

Descrizione: Ghostrunner is a cyberpunk action platformer co-developed by Slipgate Ironworks and Poland-based developer One More Level and co-published by All In! Games and 505 Games. It was released for Microsoft Windows, PlayStation 4 and Xbox One in October 2020, and Nintendo Switch in November 2020, followed by a next gen release for PlayStation 5 and Xbox Series X/S in September 2021. Ghostrunner is co-produced by 3D Realms and co-developed by Slipgate Ironworks.